SUMMARY:Country Prom Line Dance Party at The Vintage Space
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Country Prom at Vintage Space with a lively night of line dancing hosted by Grapevine Dance on March 20. Expect boots\, twirls\, and a welcoming atmosphere perfect for beginners and seasoned dancers. Lessons start at 7:30 PM so you can jump right in\, learn a few steps\, and get the night rolling. It’s the perfect midweek escape inside the Flamingo. \nBringing boots\, beats\, and community to Sonoma County\, Grapevine Dance was born when three friends saw a need for more social fun and took matters into their own hands. Partnering with local businesses\, they’ve created vibrant line dancing events where newcomers and seasoned dancers alike can kick up their heels\, connect\, and celebrate the joy of dance. What started as a hobby has grown into a thriving community\, so grab your boots and join the movement.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/country-prom-line-dance-party-at-the-vintage-space/
LOCATION:Vintage Space at The Flamingo Resort\, 2777 Fourth St.\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Other
GEO:38.45182;-122.68916
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Vintage Space at The Flamingo Resort 2777 Fourth St. Santa Rosa CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=2777 Fourth St.:geo:-122.68916,38.45182
END:VEVENT
