SUMMARY:Dan Martin and the Noma Rocksteady Band at The Elephant in the Room
DESCRIPTION:In 2010\, Dan formed The Noma Rocksteady Band to back him up\, beginning as a group of friends and local musicians that got together to share in the rocksteady vibes. By 2012 the band had solidified into a full 7-piece band\, ready to light-up dance floors everywhere. Together they have played numerous venues throughout Northern California\, and have shared the bill with such acts as The Melodians\, Burnt\, and Midnight Sun Massive. \nDan Martin and the Noma Rocksteady Band continue to lighten the spirit and shake the dance floor with old-school reggae rhythms\, while maintaining a unique contemporary sound. They were nominated for the North Bay Music Awards in 2013 for Best World/Reggae act\, and are sure to delight people of all ages. With their debut album released January 2014\, Dan and the fellas are looking forward to a great new year!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/dan-martin-and-the-noma-rocksteady-band-at-the-elephant-in-the-room/
LOCATION:Elephant in the Room\, 177A Healdsburg Avenue\, Healdsburg\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
GEO:38.60790;-122.86997
