SUMMARY:Tokes and Jokes: Mercy's Stand Up Comedy Night
DESCRIPTION:Turn up the laughs and light up the night! Join us at The Lounge at Mercy for another comedy sesh packed with killer punchlines\, chill vibes\, and clouds of good times-headlined by Phil Griffiths. Phil brings sharp wit and seasoned stand-up to the lounge. With credits opening for Kevin Nealon\, Beth Stelling\, Kyle Kinane\, and more\, expect smart\, relatable laughs all night long. \nPresented in partnership with Comedy IRL\, this smoke-filled standup session blends good buds\, great food\, and unfiltered laughter in the North Bay’s only cannabis social club. Arrive early to grab your seat\, grab a bite\, and let the good vibes roll before the show kicks off. \nSponsored By: ABX \nDate and Time:\nDate: Friday\, March 20\, 2026\nTime: 8:00 PM – 9:30 PM\nDoors Open: 6:00 PM \nTicket Tiers:\n– $25 – General Admission (Open Seating) Entry to Tokes and Jokes Open seating (first come\, first served). Come early for the best spot.\n– $35 – GA + Goodie Bag A little extra Entry + goodie bag ($20 value) included. Open seating (first come\, first served).\n– $50 – Preferred Bucket Seat + Goodie Bag Comfort upgrade Guaranteed bucket seat + shared table access\, plus goodie bag ($20 value) included. Limited seating.\n– * $75 – Preferred Bucket + Premium Bag (Most Popular) The crowd favorite * Guaranteed bucket seat + shared table access\, plus upgraded goodie bag ($50 value) included. Limited seating.\n– $100 – Preferred Bucket + VIP Bag Go big tonight Guaranteed bucket seat + shared table access\, plus loaded goodie bag ($100 value) included. Limited seating.\n– $175 – Couch Crew Pass (3 Guests + VIP Bag) Bring your crew Includes admission for 3 guests\, reserved couch seating with a dedicated table\, plus a premium bag ($150 value) included. Only 11 couches.\n– $200 – VIP Flex Pass + Elite Bag (Limited) Top-tier perks Priority seating plus elite goodie bag ($250 value) included. Very limited. \n21+ Only | DCC # C12-0000420-LIC \nURLs:\nTickets: https://go.evvnt.com/3513792-0?pid=5514\nInstagram: https://go.evvnt.com/3513792-3?pid=5514 \nDate and Time: On Fri\, 20 Mar 2026 20:00 – Fri\, 20 Mar 2026 21:30 \nVenue details: The Lounge at Mercy\, 7950 Redwood Drive\, Cotati\, California\, 94931\, United States \nCategory: Arts | Performing Arts | Comedy \nPrices:\nGeneral Admission: USD 25.00\,\nGeneral Admission + $20 Goodie Bag: USD 35.00\,\nPreferred Bucket Seat + $20 Goodie Bag: USD 50.00\,\nPreferred Bucket Seat + $50 Goodie Bag: USD 75.00\,\nPreferred Bucket + $100 Goodie Bag: USD 100.00\,\nCouch Crew Pass – 3 Guests\, Couch Seating + $150 Goodie Bag: USD 175.00\,\nVIP Flex Pass with Priority Seating + $250 Goodie Bag: USD 200.00 \nArtist: Phil Griffiths
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/tokes-and-jokes-mercys-stand-up-comedy-night-2/
LOCATION:The Lounge at Mercy\, 7950 Redwood Drive\, Cotati\, 94931
CATEGORIES:Comedy
