SUMMARY:The After Comedy Party at Barrel Proof Lounge
DESCRIPTION:Fridays | After Comedy\nAfter comedy\, Barrel Proof is NO JOKE .\nWhen the laughs end\, The After begins. DJ Dev takes control of the room with late-night energy\, a packed dance floor\, and a crowd that knows how to do Friday right.\nMore people are skipping heavy liquor and messy nights — and honestly\, same. This is the new move: Soju cocktails\, elevated mocktails\, and a club vibe that lets you party without wrecking tomorrow.\nNo sticky floors. No Jaeger on your shoes. No waking up missing your phone.\nJust great music\, fun drinks\, and a room full of people who came to look good\, feel good\, and stay out late.\n$5 Eventbrite | $10 at the door\nFree with comedy admission\n21+\nLaugh early. Dance late.\nWelcome to The After .\nCheck out www.BarrelProofLounge.com for all sorts of good times ahead!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/the-after-comedy-party-at-barrel-proof-lounge-6/
LOCATION:Barrel Proof Lounge\, 501 Mendocino Avenue\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
