SUMMARY:Spring by the River Market
DESCRIPTION:Stroll\, shop\, savor\, and soak up the energy of the season at Petaluma River Park’s first ever Spring by the River Market—a joyful intergenerational community marketplace for and by the people—happening on Saturday\, March 21st from 10am-2pm! Check out artisans\, food vendors\, multi-cultural performances\, and lots of fun activities for all ages\, celebrating the Spring Equinox and a shared vision of transforming the park into a vibrant community experience!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/spring-by-the-river-market/
