SUMMARY:Saturday Live Music at Spicy Vines feat. Cello Joe
DESCRIPTION:Where unforgettable wines\, live music\, and good vibes come together. \nJoin us every Saturday from 3–6 PM at Spicy Vines for a tasting room experience like no other — where top local musicians from across the Bay Area meet our award-winning small-lot wines. From Rock & Roll and Blues to Jazz\, Bluegrass\, and Americana\, each weekend brings new sounds and new reasons to raise a glass. \nCello Joe\nCello Joe is the world’s only beatboxing\, long-distance-bicycle-touring cellist\, mixing classical training with live looping\, hip-hop\, funk\, and folk to create a truly original sound. \nDetails\nNo cover. Walk-ins are welcome\, but this event tends to fill up quickly\, so we recommend making a reservation. We are dog and family friendly!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/saturday-live-music-at-spicy-vines-feat-cello-joe-2/
LOCATION:Spicy Vines\, 441 Healdsburg Ave.\, Healdsburg\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
