SUMMARY:“Emergence” - Spring Though the Eyes of the Artists
DESCRIPTION:The Artists of Fulton Crossing invite you to celebrate Spring though Art.\nOpening Reception March 21st\, 4-7pm\nLive Music and Refreshments\n“Emergence” brings together the Artists of Fulton Crossing to explore what Spring means to their creative lives. Spring is more than a season. It is a metaphor. It’s renewal\, risk\, color\, thawing\, blooming\, awakening\, and sometimes even struggles. The public is invited to come meet the artists and enjoy this free art exhibit\, artists studios and gallery spaces.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/emergence-spring-though-the-eyes-of-the-artists/
LOCATION:Fulton Crossing Artisan Studios & Gallery\, 1200 River Rd\, Fulton\, CA
CATEGORIES:Art
